data.description: Perfect location to be near the happenings in Conway! Split floor plan, 10' ceilings in living room and formal dining room. Need a place for an office? The formal dining room can easily be used for just that! Spacious primary bedroom with tray ceilings, bath features separate walk in shower and jet tub. Covered back patio area and fenced in backyard. This is a must see!
